				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-6358012/to-never-again-see-the-light-of-day#post-3869497</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Wed, 11 Jul 2018 00:01:55 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Yossipossi</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2199269</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p><em>In restless dreams I walked alone<br /> Narrow streets of cobblestone<br /> 'Neath the halo of a street lamp<br /> I turned my collar to the cold and damp<br /> When my eyes were stabbed by the flash of a neon light<br /> That split the night<br /> And touched the sound of <strong>silence</strong>.</em></p> <p>All jokes aside, this is amazing. I can't wait to see more of the Department of Abnormalities. +1.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
